					<h2>
A Ritual Carried Forward</h2>				
		<p>Even today, these gestures and formulas remain a living testament to the ancestral expertise of the women of Al Ain. Each application is an invitation to slow down, reconnect with oneself, and embrace a beauty legacy that transcends generations.</p><p>LUMA does not simply create skincare products. It preserves a way of life where nature and tradition unite to reveal each woman’s unique radiance.</p><p>A secret to be shared, a tradition to be honored, a heritage to be continued.</p>		
